  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Constants
    A series of constants used throughout the project.
    DataTag
    This class provides an easy way to represent and read pairs of data.
    DynamicCompiler
    This class was copied from the location below and was created by david, the author of the article.
    DynamicCompiler.InMemoryJavaFileObject
    java File Object represents an in-memory java source file
    so there is no need to put the source file on hard disk
    DynamicCompiler.MyDiagnosticListener
    This class will print diagnostic information about any failed compilations.
    Log
    This is a very rudimentary logging system.
    MinMax
    This is a utility class used to simplify the process of keeping track and getting the minimum and maximum values of a set of numerical data.
    Parameters
    This class is meant to simplify the process of storing and loading various parameters from files by proving useful utility methods and constructors.
    Point
    This class was created as an alternative to the standard util.Point class Java provides because those points only store Integer locations, when Double locations were needed.
    Utils
    A series of public static methods that are written to provide utility to other classes
    Vector2
    This class stores a 2 dimensional Vector and provides a few methods for manipulating that vector.
